</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel id="A21357B4FFBBFFCAA87F5C2E5B0E53B4" box="[531,621,1896,1922]" pageId="9" pageNumber="10" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
♂. 
<emphasis id="B920EACFFFBBFFCAA8FB5C215BCF53B7" bold="true" box="[663,684,1895,1921]" pageId="9" pageNumber="10">A</emphasis>
. Body in dorsal view. 
<emphasis id="B920EACFFFBBFFCAA9DC5C215AA753B7" bold="true" box="[944,964,1895,1921]" pageId="9" pageNumber="10">B</emphasis>
. Face. 
<emphasis id="B920EACFFFBBFFCAAE7B5C215D4F53B7" bold="true" box="[1047,1068,1895,1921]" pageId="9" pageNumber="10">C</emphasis>
. Pro- and mesothoracic legs in ventral view. 
<emphasis id="B920EACFFFBBFFCAAB125CCC58D25392" bold="true" box="[382,433,1930,1956]" pageId="9" pageNumber="10">D-E</emphasis>
. Metathoracic leg. 
<emphasis id="B920EACFFFBBFFCAA8F45CCC5BCE5392" bold="true" box="[664,685,1930,1956]" pageId="9" pageNumber="10">D</emphasis>
